"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-06-olympian-wins-lifetime-supply-ramen-macaroni-cheese-gold-medal-win-21372029\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Carlos Yulo\\u00a0made history when he won gold for the Philippines at theParisOlympics- and will receive a lifetime supply of some tasty treats as a reward.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 151, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 11, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}, {\"begin\": 50, \"end\": 61, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 0.9999995364879561, \"rank\": 4.2102547199533607e-07, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Philippines have only ever won three gold medals at the Olympics, with gymnastics star Yulo responsible for two of them.\", \"from\": 153, \"to\": 277, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 157, \"end\": 168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 0.9999995364879561, \"rank\": 4.2102547199533607e-07, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He won the men's floor and vault events at the 2024 games, turning him into an overnight sensation in his country.\", \"from\": 279, \"to\": 393, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow\\u00a0Metro.co.uk's live blog for updates from the Paris 2024 Olympics  But as well as having the honour of being a two-time Olympic gold medalist, the 24-year-old is also in line to receive several incredible gifts when he returns home.\", \"from\": 395, \"to\": 633, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Philippine government are reportedly awarding 10 million pesos (over \\u00a3136,000) to any of their gold medalists from Paris, in addition to 6 million pesos (over \\u00a381,000) in cash incentives from their\\u00a0House of Representatives.\", \"from\": 635, \"to\": 862, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 639, \"end\": 660, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_the_Philippines\", \"score\": 0.5824905611208986, \"rank\": 0.7167660160460866, \"text\": \"Philippine government\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_the_Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_the_Philippines\"}, {\"begin\": 754, \"end\": 759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999849933, \"rank\": 1.510065365569401e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it's local businesses that have promised Yulo the most eye-catching gifts, with a real estate firm offering him a fully furnished three-bedroom property in a prestigious area of the coastal city of Taguig.\", \"from\": 864, \"to\": 1073, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 909, \"end\": 913, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5699066707590952e-24, \"text\": \"Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}, {\"begin\": 1066, \"end\": 1072, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taguig\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.000117738105313e-15, \"text\": \"Taguig\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taguig\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taguig\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A lifetime supply of ramen also awaits courtesy of the Hagemu Sushi and Ramen Bar in Calasiao, who posted onFacebook: 'Congratulations to our very own Golden Boy on clinching his second gold medal in men's artistic gymnastics!\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1301, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1137, \"end\": 1142, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sushi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.960681702976696e-20, \"text\": \"Sushi\", \"types\": [\"Q2095\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sushi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sushi\"}, {\"begin\": 1160, \"end\": 1168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Calasiao\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Calasiao\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Calasiao\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Calasiao\"}, {\"begin\": 1226, \"end\": 1236, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Golden_Boy_Promotions\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.141573302527515e-20, \"text\": \"Golden Boy\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Golden_Boy_Promotions\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Golden_Boy_Promotions\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'To celebrate your outstanding achievement, we are thrilled to extend a special gift: FREE LIFETIME RAMEN not just for you, but also for your wonderful and supportive girlfriend, Chloe Anjeleigh.\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1498, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Enjoy the taste of victory and love with every bowl!'\", \"from\": 1500, \"to\": 1554, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Other restaurant chains will gift him endless amounts of macaroni cheese and grilled chicken.\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1649, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On the over end of the scale, a gastroenterologist has offered free consultations and colonoscopies for life.\", \"from\": 1651, \"to\": 1760, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I was just hoping to perform well.\", \"from\": 1762, \"to\": 1797, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not really expect a medal,' Yulo said after winning his golds.\", \"from\": 1798, \"to\": 1866, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1832, \"end\": 1836, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5699066707590952e-24, \"text\": \"Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It really felt like a bonus for me.\", \"from\": 1868, \"to\": 1904, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's crazy, because last night [Saturday] I could not sleep.\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 1965, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'It still did not sink in.\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 1993, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This morning I was so sleepy.\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2023, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not know what to do.\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2050, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I did it today.'\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2071, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 2073, \"to\": 2121, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 2123, \"to\": 2193, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:'It's a scandal!'\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2222, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"- Olympian blasts penalty for every French medallist at Paris 2024  ArrowMORE:'I will not get them!'\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2323, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2259, \"end\": 2265, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8714585151712753, \"rank\": 0.14355709189401258, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2279, \"end\": 2289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999993179, \"rank\": 6.319970797874984e-13, \"text\": \"Par